com.samsung.android.sdk.pen.document

Class SpenPath

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.samsung.android.sdk.pen.document.SpenPath

  • public class SpenPath
extends Object
    Path class in Pen SDK.
    You can get the SpenPath instance from SpenObjectShape or SpenObjectLine, but you cannot change values of this and cannot set a path to objects.
